Package au.edu.anu.rscs.aot.queries.base

Class IfThenQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • au.edu.anu.rscs.aot.queries.QueryAdaptor
      • au.edu.anu.rscs.aot.queries.base.IfThenQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Queryable
    public class IfThenQuery
extends QueryAdaptor

    Test query. If this Query is satisfied, applies a query (called trueQuery), and if not, applies another one (called falseQuery) to the submit() argument.

    Type of input to submit()
    any class compatible with the constructor query arguments;
    Type of result
    the result of trueQuery or falseQuery, depending on the outcome of the test query
    Author:
    Shayne Flint - 26/3/2012
